{
  "stem": "27443.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am coming back, because I'm a Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they let me go back to the train to go to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I arrived this way to Prague.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I arrived to Prague, it was the IRO, the international Refugee Organization, the IRO, and the Jewish Federation, and the UNRWA took care-- there was also the [? gemeente, ?] and there was all the officers.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went there, and we were fed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I met a certain someone in-- in the Jewish Federation that remembered me from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My family.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said that they were liberated to [NON-ENGLISH] a few weeks ago, and they thought that they saw my father there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I boarded a train that same night to [NON-ENGLISH], from Prague.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I arrived to [NON-ENGLISH], I uncovered the thousands of bodies, looking for my father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But unfortunately, I couldn't find anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was there two days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after two days, I went back to Prague.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From Prague, we formed a whole group of young girls and boys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And from the Jewish Federation, from the UNRWA, they transported us to Salzburg, Austria.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was a displaced persons camp in Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When we arrived into camp in Austria, we had food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a novelty to us, because after the liberation, whatever came under my hand, I ate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we came into camp in Salzburg, and we were all young boys and girls my age.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were there a few weeks, that came a group of [HEBREW] from Israel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they all introduced ourselves to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they gave us lectures, and they said to us, you are not [NON-ENGLISH], my kids.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You have a land of Palestine.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
